# HeroUI v3

This project uses **HeroUI version 3** (`@heroui/react` and `@heroui/styles`).

- Prefer HeroUI v3 components for buttons, forms, modals, popovers, inputs, etc.
- Import from `@heroui/react` (e.g. `Button`, `Popover`, `Input`, `Surface`, `Toast`).
- Follow the v3 API: e.g. `Popover` has no `placement` on the root; use `Popover.Content` with `placement`. Use component APIs as in the [HeroUI v3 docs](https://www.heroui.com/).
